column2: Make music or dance to honor Eir.

Help Assistant Foreman Kofi keep the people of the Gladefields safe.

Many thanks for demonstrating the finer points of basic housekeeping and pest control to my royal retinue. Your humble station in life has obviously proven educational—you clean and kill with the efficiency of a company of mummies. You have my gratitude, commoner.

—Prince Bakkal
